{"tid":471972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中年漢疑搞婚外情 撼頭埋牆自殺","createTime":"2017-11-17T18:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T01:59:39.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da94de92e4cbdb2da16774476d406f2019fcfef0","tid":471972,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:03:04.000Z","msg":"<strong>中年漢疑搞婚外情 撼頭埋牆自殺</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-11-18 00:53:09 HKT<br />\n<br />\n昨晚11時許，將軍澳尚德邨尚明樓，一名50多歲男子疑婚外情，與妻子發生爭執，男子拆去廁所馬桶蓋扑頭企圖自殺，並撼頭埋牆，以致頭破血流受傷昏迷，家人制止並報警。救護員到場送伊利沙伯醫院救治，其後回復清醒。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e2fa8e2c555100b491bf62ddde5f2b81a1888c","tid":471972,"uid":8922,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:04:37.000Z","msg":"傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3316a12204ae010d33da52f3f97bb11ea274bf","tid":471972,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"又一弱智上報"},{"pid":"baab7178b8a3f837e1b366881e481d0df1e60e7a","tid":471972,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:05:04.000Z","msg":"死唔去變癡呆先慘"},{"pid":"14d2c8d8169bc9bbd4c40c717f707753325b3976","tid":471972,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死唔去變癡呆先慘</blockquote><br />\n本身都⋯"},{"pid":"7f101ecd4860e4c9dd71c821d9942c12991f15e5","tid":471972